</ul>
<p><strong>History</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Naming: after Roman Tellus, deity of the Earth</li>
<li>Discovery: Franz-Joseph Müller von Reichenstein (1782)</li>
<li>First isolation: Martin Heinrich Klaproth</li>
</ul>
